data.description: Welcome to this beautiful brick colonial nestled in the charming enclave of North Wilmington. Perfectly situated on a serene cul-de-sac, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence boasts over 2,200 sq ft of timeless elegance. The lower level welcomes you with gleaming hardwood floors throughout, setting the stage for a lifestyle of comfort and style.  Step into the formal living and dining rooms, where the classic charm of each space is accentuated by natural light pouring in through large windows. The eat-in kitchen is a culinary haven, offering a perfect blend of functionality and style. A second living area with a beautiful wood-burning fireplace creates a cozy retreat for gatherings or quiet evenings.  Convenience is key on the lower level, featuring a half bath and a strategically placed washer and dryer, making daily living a breeze. This level also provides easy access to the oversized attached two-car garage, ensuring your vehicles are sheltered in style, and access to the beautiful backyard.  Venture outside to discover a beautiful, huge backyard that invites you to unwind and entertain. The expansive deck provides the perfect setting for al fresco dining or enjoying the tranquility of your outdoor oasis.  Ascend the stairs to the second level, where four generously sized bedrooms await, each offering abundant space and natural light. The Primary Bedroom is a luxurious sanctuary, equipped with a full bath for moments of relaxation. The hall provides access to another recently updated full bathroom, showcasing modern amenities and tasteful design.  The surprises continue with a big full unfinished basement, offering endless possibilities. This additional space opens the door to potential uses such as a recreation room, home gym, or even a home office, allowing you to tailor this residence to meet your unique needs.  With a perfect blend of classic charm, modern updates, a stunning outdoor retreat, and a versatile full basement, this North Wilmington gem invites you to experience a lifestyle of elegance and convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously maintained residence your home. Schedule a showing today and step into a world of refined living.
